Get the cell assignment probabilities of a cellassign fit

cellprobs.Rd

Get the MLE cell type assignment probabilities for each cell

cellprobs(x)

# S3 method for cellassign
cellprobs(x)

Arguments

x

An object of class cellassign returned by a call to cellassign(...)

Value

A cell by celltype matrix with assignment probabilities

Examples

data(example_cellassign_fit)
cellprobs(example_cellassign_fit)
